000;\\\">&raquo; C&aacute;ch 2<\\/span>: \\u0110\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c&aacute;ch th\\u1ee9 2 n&agrave;y, anh em h&atilde;y d\\u1ef1a v&agrave;o ngay k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ee7a gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t n\\u1ed5 ra v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y th\\u1ee9 2. C&aacute;ch th\\u1ee9c th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n. Anh em ch\\u1ec9 vi\\u1ec7c l\\u1ea5y con s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti&ecirc;n c\\u1ee7a d&atilde;y s\\u1ed1 gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y th\\u1ee9 2 \\u0111\\u1ec3 l&agrave;m s\\u1ed1 nu&ocirc;i trong nguy&ecirc;n 1 tu\\u1ea7n k\\u1ebf ti\\u1ebfp.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ee0000;\\\">&raquo; C&aacute;ch 3<\\/span>: \\u0110\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi c&aacute;ch th\\u1ee9 3, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ch\\u01a1i c\\u1ea7n theo d&otilde;i k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ee7a gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t v&agrave;i ng&agrave;y th\\u1ee9 2. V&agrave; r\\u1ed3i, anh em h&atilde;y k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p 2 con s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti&ecirc;n c\\u1ee7a gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t ng&agrave;y th\\u1ee9 2 v&agrave; ng&agrave;y th\\u1ee9 3. C\\u0169ng c&oacute; th\\u1ec3, anh em h&atilde;y l\\u1ea5y t\\u1ed5ng 2 s\\u1ed1 n&agrave;y \\u0111\\u1ec3 l&agrave;m t\\u1ed5ng chu\\u1ea9n. \\u0110\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c&aacute;ch &agrave;m n&agrave;y, anh em n&ecirc;n nu&ocirc;i l&ocirc; trong l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u1eddi gian t\\u1eeb 5 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 7 ng&agrave;y nh\\u1eb1m n\\u0103ng cao c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i chi\\u1ebfn th\\u1eafng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><\\/p>\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; color: #008000;\\\">Soi c\\u1ea7u theo ki\\u1ec3u b\\u1ea1ch th\\u1ee7<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>\\u0110\\u1ebfn v\\u1edbi c&aacute;ch soi c\\u1ea7u mi\\u1ec1n B\\u1eafc d\\u1ef1a v&agrave;o b\\u1ea1ch th\\u1ee7 s\\u1ebd l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph&aacute;p nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ecbnh anh em kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n b\\u1ecf qua. \\u0110\\u01b0\\u1ee3c bi\\u1ebft, \\u0111&acirc;y l&